title: NBA Impersonator @BdotAdot5 Kevin Garnett Impression
text:
You've seen his masterful work as Kobe Bryant . You've laughed at his spot-on impression of Russell Westbrook . The Sacramento Kings got him to do a solid version of Jason "White Chocolate" Williams . Basically, every time @BdotAdot5 gives us a new video of another NBA star, past and present, dude doesn't miss.
His most recent work of art comes in the form of Kevin Garnett . From "accidentally" getting locked up with his opponents to his pregame ritual to his unique jumper, BdotAdot5 has got him down to a T. Check it out.
Send all complaints, compliments, and tips to sportstips@complex.com
